OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,FOur Scottish Politics Correspondent
OL,7,FOliver Wright reports:
OL,9,FOliver Wright continues his analysis:
OL,11,FThey say you can't make an omelette
OL,12,Fwithout breaking a few eggs. And the
OL,13,FScottish Government certainly seems to
OL,14,Fbe cracking them by the dozen when it
OL,15,Fcomes to its policy on food prices.
OL,17,FThe SNP's election promise to cap the
OL,18,Fprice of up to 50 essential food items
OL,19,Fhas been met with a chorus of
OL,20,Fcriticism.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,FAt first glance, it might be hard to
OL,7,Fsee why.
OL,9,FThe cost of living has been the number
OL,10,Fone concern for voters over the last
OL,11,Ffew years - and this election pledge
OL,12,Fmight be one way to tackle that. In
OL,13,Ffact, it was the perhaps the only
OL,14,Fmemorable flagship policy of any of
OL,15,Fthe parties in the election campaign.
OL,17,FThe SNP administration wants to limit
OL,18,Fthe price retailers are able to charge
OL,19,Fthe consumer for a "basket of
OL,20,Fessential food items" like milk, eggs
OL,21,Fand bread.
OL,26,@{D@TOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,FBut for the farmers producing those
OL,7,Fessentials, a price cap just gives
OL,8,Fthem another challenge to contend with.
OL,10,FThe last few years has been
OL,11,Fexceptionally difficult for those
OL,12,Fworking in the agriculture sector.
OL,14,FThe war in Ukraine pushed up fuel and
OL,15,Ffertiliser prices. Unexpected poor
OL,16,Fweather led to lower crop yields.
OL,17,FSupermarket price volatility has left
OL,18,Ffarmers gambling more than ever. And
OL,19,Fthe war in Iran pushed fuel prices up
OL,20,Ffurther still.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,F"Farming is now becoming increasingly
OL,7,Fchallenging," says Annabel Hamilton, a
OL,8,Ffarmer based near Coldingham.
OL,10,F"We're seeing huge price volatility
OL,11,Fwithin the livestock and the cereal
OL,12,Fmarkets.
OL,14,F"That is making my job increasingly
OL,15,Fmore interesting as we go forward."
OL,17,FThe prospect of a price cap proves to
OL,18,Fbe just another challenge to add to
OL,19,Fthe mix.
OL,21,F"It's a bit scary, actually.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@MO]rD@AOUvD@AOUwD@cO]}D@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,F"The Scottish Government feel like
OL,7,Fthat's something that needs to be
OL,8,Fbrought in.
OL,10,F"I understand that everybody should
OL,11,Fhave access to healthy food, but at
OL,12,Fthe same time, it's the farmers that
OL,13,Fare going to feel the real effect of
OL,14,Fthat capping.
OL,16,F"We have a certain cost of production.
OL,18,F"We have a price that we need to be
OL,19,Fable to sell our produce, to be able
OL,20,Fto make that profitability that's
OL,21,Frequired for the business.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,F"And not knowing where that is going
OL,7,Fto be for a lot of the time, is a hard
OL,8,Fway to farm."
OL,10,FIt's a concern shared by the body
OL,11,Frepresenting farmers across Scotland.
OL,13,FRobert Neill, Vice President for NFU
OL,14,FScotland warned putting more pressure
OL,15,Fon farmers may drive them to pack it
OL,16,Fin altogether.
OL,18,FHe said: "We are the primary producer
OL,19,Fand we are price takers, not price
OL,20,Fsetters, which we need to change.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@MO]zD@JOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,F"A lot of the food that we are
OL,7,Fproducing is below the cost of
OL,8,Fproduction, and we're not being
OL,9,Frewarded for that.
OL,11,F"How does that stack up?
OL,13,F"There's going to be a lot of farmers
OL,14,Ffeeling the pinch and probably go out
OL,15,Fof business."
OL,17,FIt is not just those producing the
OL,18,Ffood that we put on our tables that
OL,19,Fhave concerns about how this price cap
OL,20,Fwill work in practice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,FThe Scottish Retail Consortium
OL,7,Fdescribed the policy as a "gimmick"
OL,8,Fbefore the Holyrood Election.
OL,10,FThe Food and Drink Federation said it
OL,11,F"risked undermining investment" and
OL,12,Fcould cause a "flood of cheap imports."
OL,14,FAnd it's been met with resounding
OL,15,Fcondemnation from opposition parties
OL,16,Fat Holyrood - although that is
OL,17,Funsurprising.
OL,26,@oD@[OUoD@cO]sD@AOUsD@_O]tD@OOUtD@gO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,FPreviously, First Minister John
OL,7,FSwinney defended the pledge after
OL,8,Fconcerns were raised that it could be
OL,9,Fblocked by the UK altogether as it
OL,10,Fwould require changes to the Internal
OL,11,FMarket Act.
OL,13,FIndeed, previous plans to introduce a
OL,14,Fsimilar, but voluntary, cap from the
OL,15,FUK Government were dropped after a
OL,16,Fconcerted backlash from the
OL,17,Fsupermarket industry. This cap won't
OL,18,Fbe voluntary.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,FA Scottish Government spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "The planned food price cap is
OL,8,Fintended to help people with the cost
OL,9,Fof living by keeping costs low on
OL,10,Fessential foods such as bread, milk,
OL,11,Feggs and other items.
OL,13,F"The Scottish Government regularly
OL,14,Fengages with the food and drink
OL,15,Findustry, retailers and producers and
OL,16,Fwill continue to do so as these
OL,17,Fproposals, including how it is
OL,18,Fimplemented and operated, develop.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,F"Further details will be announced in
OL,7,Fdue course but our intention remains
OL,8,Fto publish draft legislative
OL,9,Fprovisions within the first 100 days
OL,10,Fof this government."
OL,12,FRising costs have made life more
OL,13,Fdifficult for everyone across the
OL,14,Fregion.
OL,26,@rD@TO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,FAnd while the Scottish Government has
OL,7,Fcome under heavy fire for this policy,
OL,8,Fit does provide a tangible way in
OL,9,Fwhich John Swinney's administration
OL,10,Fcan be seen to be doing something
OL,11,Fabout it. Delivering that policy,
OL,12,Fthough, will take an enormous amount
OL,13,Fof work.
OL,15,FThat task will fall on the shoulders
OL,16,Fof Stephen Flynn, the new Economy
OL,17,FSecretary. He's new to Holyrood after
OL,18,Fgiving up his seat at Westminster.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784141288
OL,3,CScottish farmers warn supermarket
OL,4,Cprice cap could destroy them
OL,6,FIt's quite the to-do list: balancing
OL,7,Fkeeping this election promise while
OL,8,Fprotecting farmers and retailers, and
OL,9,Fdealing with any legal challenges from
OL,10,FWestminster. Flynn was always
OL,11,Fambitious heading into Government.
OL,12,FGetting this over the line will
OL,13,Fcertainly put his ambition to the test.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/13
